9. b3{ It is very awkward for Black to complete his development. He clearly will not get  f5 - f4  in, and as such, the whole  f7 - f5  business doesn't make much sense. Additionally, his bishop can never make it to  e6  on pain of  d4 - d5 ,  e5 - e4  is always met with  f2 - f3 , and White just looks better to me. A logical follow-up would likely be  Bc1 - b2 ,  Qd1 - d2  and rooks to  d1  and  e1  next. Someday he can hope to abuse the  d5 -square. }
