9. d4
10. Nb5{ White is much better thanks to his active pieces and Black's poorly placed king. White has endless ideas to increase the pressure, including  c4 - c5  followed by  Nb5 - d6  to smash the queenside, or  O-O  and  f2 - f4  to smash the center. }
