11. Rc1
11. Rfc8
12. Ne1{ I really like this idea. In general, I think Black's only hope to fight for equality with this setup is to get  b7 - b5  through. The best way to deal with this plan might be to swing the knight to  d3  and always be ready with  c4 - c5  in time. Furthermore, it also works really well against a ... Qh5  plan since ... Bh3  will never be possible. }
