13. Nd3{ Black will not be able to easily get his normal plan with  a7 - a6 ,  Ra8 - b8 , and  b7 - b5  through. In the meantime,  c4 - c5  is always an idea. }
13. Rab8( 13...a6?! 14.c5! { I like this direct move. Black is in big trouble thanks to the activity. } )
14. b3
