11. Nxd4( 11...exd6 12.Ndb5± { Black will soon be relieved of his  d6 -pawn, and White's pieces will remain active and menacing. White is clearly better. } )
12. dxe7{ I like clipping a pawn as an in-between move. }
12. Qxe7
