6. e6{ Nowadays, this is considered to be Black's biggest mainline in the Symmetrical English. He aims to play a Fischer Setup, but by waiting on  e7 - e6  for a move, he denies us the chance to sacrifice a pawn and play for the initiative with  d2 - d4 . }
