ys lost. }31...Qe6 32.Qxe6 fxe6 33.Rxd6 Kf7 34.Rd7+ Kf8 35.Rg7 ( 35.Be5  ) )27.Qxe7 { No way Black survives this. }27...Nc3 ( 27...Qf5 28.g4 Qf4  )28.Qf6  )( {  3.    }25...Bd7! { This is a computer move if I have ever seen one. } )
